reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works great to take your screws out of your ring doorbell
reviews.reviewText: I recently had to do some work and re-sync my ring doorbell I needed to screw out of the bottom of the cover to get out my ring doorbell. The screw that’s used is super small and doesn’t work very well and is easily stripped. I was able to use this tool, the small side to get the screw out that was stripped then use the replacement screws that was given with this kit to use the bigger head and put a new screw into the ring doorbell so that I will not have this issue of stripping the screw when I take it back out again if I need to take the cover off. Highly commend the products for the price

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lots of screws of varying type, plus the tool
reviews.reviewText: The reason I bought this kit was to change the screw on the bottom of my Chamberlain MyQ video keypad, to reduce the chances of somebody stealing it. I swapped out the factory Phillips head screw with a number six flathead torx screw from this kit that requires a special tool to remove. I feel very confident now that my video keypad is relatively theft proof, or at least theft resistant.
